001package org.example.triviaucab1;
002
003import javafx.application.Application;
004import javafx.fxml.FXMLLoader;
005import javafx.scene.Scene;
006import javafx.stage.Stage;
007
008import java.io.IOException;
009
010public class MainPrincipal extends Application {
011    @Override
012    public void start(Stage stage) throws IOException {
013        FXMLLoader fxmlLoader = new FXMLLoader(getClass().getResource("MenuPrincipalView.fxml"));
014        Scene scene = new Scene(fxmlLoader.load());
015        stage.setTitle("TRIVIA UCAB - Men√∫ Principal");
016        stage.setScene(scene);
017        stage.setFullScreen(true);
018        stage.show();
019    }
020    public static void main(String[] args) {
021        launch();
022    }
023}
